{"tid":974501,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲比ex hurt過之後 第二段感情好似有創傷後遺症咁？","createTime":"2019-01-09T02:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T17:31:10.000Z","uid":14090,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"16308c2092139de08d94f97141459d166468ce02","tid":974501,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:29:11.000Z","msg":"我成日好驚會有第二次發生，但其實明明依家佢乜都冇做過<br />\n<br />\n情況好似創傷後遺症咁，搞到自己過份緊張，有時仲逼到對方太緊，搞到對方好攰，好似忽略咗佢咁 依家佢想分開冷靜一排<br />\n<br />\n其實我唔係唔信任佢，只不過有種感覺我係控制唔到，可能第一段感情比人hurt得好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想知可以點控制？始終咁樣對大家都唔好，不如趁依家冷靜緊，想改變一下，改變一下自己心態，因為始終咁樣影響到佢都有啲唔公平，我好似先入為主咗咁。希望改變下，大家長遠先有得發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：我好愛好愛佢 唔想佢離開我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4ee2d849e3fc5080e2d3ac3074c0a24be12cdf","tid":974501,"uid":148321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:31:51.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n搞到迫得太緊"},{"pid":"40fc322bde98e1aae474c4de74e96ec7ae5f1c46","tid":974501,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:31:58.000Z","msg":"創傷後遺症好似好誇張咁<br />\n<br />\n同啲軍人既創傷後遺症比 我呢啲唔算得係咩 但得諗唔到可以點形容 個情況真係同創傷後遺症差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decb056ce3fff6bd5258c4f47c1540d0ad69e03d","tid":974501,"uid":14090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a4ee2d849e3fc5080e2d3ac3074c0a24be12cdf","tid":974501,"uid":148321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:31:51.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n搞到迫得太緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T02:32:28.000Z","msg":"我都係 成日check住對方 好似好無安全感咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f29dbac3ec2339144277d00500d88081528dd92","tid":974501,"uid":148321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"decb056ce3fff6bd5258c4f47c1540d0ad69e03d","tid":974501,"uid":14090,"like":1,"dislike"